
flowchart LR
    subgraph VM2["VM 2"]
        TP[Third Party] -->|drops .log files| LD[Log Directory]
        C2[Container 2<br/>Log Collector]
        LD -->|watches| C2
        C2 -->|processes & sends| Queue
    end
    
    subgraph VM1["VM 1"]
        C1[Container 1<br/>Log Processor]
        DB[(Database)]
        Queue -->|pulls logs| C1
        C1 -->|parses & stores| DB
    end
    
    VM2 -.->|VPN Connection| VM1